reviewText: I would not recommend paying specifically for this course. It is generally useful but the course needs to be updated to reflect the changes made by Microsoft to the AZ-900 exam in May 2022. The 50% discount for the exam is no longer available  (since over a year according to comments in the discussion forum). The same content is available for free (and up to date) on the Microsoft learn website.
Good for be introduced to these services on Microsoft Azure. Would be more complete with more hands-on exercices, but still I will recommend to do it.
Excellent introduction to the topic with excellent delivery.
Not as interesting as the second course, but the information in this course is very valuable
This is the Best AZ-900 Course in Microsoft Azure

This is a great program, to start up my new  career in IT.

This was very educating and simplified, like teaching a toddler. Concepts are well brought forward.
